  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Kayne, the sole survivor of the Wolf Squadron, is tasked with saving the Vorn which is being attacked from the nefarious Kotan-Kal. For offering to help the Vorn out, Kayne is given his choice of the Vorn's most advanced spacecraft and weapons.\n\nIn this space combat game, Kayne has the choice of 1 of 9 different spacecrafts which differ in appearance, weaponry, and control. Kayne is tasked with completing 40 different missions while fighting 37 different types of enemy crafts, which include bounty hunters, crime spaceships and military ships.",
